        Backup Offers in Queensland Property Sales: A Seller's Guide
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A well-handled backup offer can save weeks of campaign time and tens of thousands of dollars if a primary contract falls over. Here is how backup offers work in Queensland, when to accept one, and the common traps sellers need to avoid.
      </p>
    </div>
